## 🎨 Theme Customization

The site uses CSS custom properties for easy theme customization:

```css
:root {
    --primary-dark: #0a0a0a;
    --cyan-primary: #00ffff;
    --neon-pink: #ff00ff;
    --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan-primary), var(--neon-pink));
}
```

